nodes.text: Timothy M. Rose (born July 17, 1956) is an American puppeteer best known for playing Admiral Ackbar in Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi, Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens and Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi.
